{"id":315951,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/【图说天朝】身教胜于言传/","date":"2013-09-30T08:05:15Z","modified":"2013-10-05T00:15:06Z","title":"【图说天朝】身教胜于言传","content":"<p>近日，济南趵突泉边，一个一岁半的宝宝把酸奶盒扔到了水里。“多清澈的泉水呀，你这么做对不对呀？”年轻妈妈一边教育宝宝，一边借工具捞酸奶盒。她坚持用伞把勾了十多次，一番周折后最终把盒子捞了上来，放在了宝宝车后的垃圾箱里。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-315951 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e8%ba%ab%e6%95%99%e8%83%9c%e4%ba%8e%e8%a8%80%e4%bc%a0/attachment/1992842835211496957/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/1992842835211496957-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/1992842835211496957-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/1992842835211496957-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e8%ba%ab%e6%95%99%e8%83%9c%e4%ba%8e%e8%a8%80%e4%bc%a0/attachment/6598112103681292925/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/6598112103681292925-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" s